quran[5]{c,v,t}:
  97,1,“Ndithu taivumbulutsa (Qur’an) mu usiku wa Qadr (usiku wolemekezeka)
  97,2,“Ndi chiyani chingakudziwitse za usiku wolemekezekawu
  97,3,“Usiku olemekezekawu uli wabwino kuposa miyezi chikwi chimodzi ( yomwe mulibe Laila-tul-Qadr)
  97,4,“Amatsika angelo ndi Jiburil mmenemo mwa chilolezo cha Mbuye wawo kudzalongosola chinthu chilichonse
  97,5,“Mtendere usiku umenewo! (Palibe mavuto ndi zoipa) mpaka m’bandakucha